Edition:
Quote: Suppliers content that there is enough milk consigned by the Hutt line to necessitate the use of cool vans to maintain the good quality of milk for city consumers, and it is urged that an open wool truck, with temporary covers, as used for excursion passengers, should be provided till the very conservative Department has agreed, in the interests of public health, to put on a proper van.
